        "15d9d2f4-1bdd-49c8-9a99-58246020f05c": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Pre Sale Questions",
            "question_1": "Q1: “Is this product compatible with my vehicle?”",
            "answer_1": "<p>A1: Please refer to the compatibility details provided on the product page. \n<br>If you are still unsure, feel free to contact us via live chat or email at  <a href=\"mailto:support@teslaunch.net\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">support@teslaunch.net</a>.</p>",
            "question_2": "Q2: “How long will delivery take after placing an order?”",
            "answer_2": "<p>A2: Our standard delivery time is 6-12 days. For some products, delivery may take as little as 3-7 days. Please note that delivery times may vary slightly based on your location and any unforeseen logistical circumstances.</p>",
            "question_3": "Q3: “Which countries do you ship to?”",
            "answer_3": "<p>A3: We offer worldwide shipping.\n</p><p>Exclusions:\n Please note that P.O. Box addresses are accepted (excluding APO/FPO/DPO addresses). Kindly provide a residential or business address during checkout.</p>",
            "question_4": "Q4: “Who is responsible for customs duties and taxes?”",
            "answer_4": "<p>A4: Each country or region has its own customs regulations and policies. Please contact your local customs office for more details. In rare cases, if import duties or taxes are incurred, they are the responsibility of the customer.</p>",
            "question_5": "Q5: “Which payment methods are supported?”",
            "answer_5": "<p>A5: Payment Methods include:\n PayPal Express, Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover, Diners Club, Apple Pay, Bancontact, Google Pay, IDEAL, and Shop Pay.\n</p>",
            "question_6": "Q6: “How is payment security ensured?”",
            "answer_6": "<p>A6: We utilize advanced encryption and secure payment gateways to protect your personal and financial information. Your security is our top priority.\n</p>",
