        "paragraph_7XUYzr": {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "title": "After-Sale Questions",
            "question_1": "Q1:\"How do I install the product?\"",
            "answer_1": "<p>A1: Please refer to the installation video available on the product page or the instructions included in the package. \n<br>If you need further assistance, feel free to contact our customer support at <a href=\"mailto:support@teslaunch.net\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">support@teslaunch.net</a>.</p>",
            "question_2": "Q2:\"How do I request a return or refund?\"",
            "answer_2": "<p>A2: Please contact our customer support team at <a href=\"mailto:support@teslaunch.net\" to=\"\" initiate=\"\" the=\"\" process.style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">support@teslaunch.net</a>.</p>",
            "question_3": "Q3:\"What is your refund policy?\"",
            "answer_3": "<p>A3: We have a 30-day return policy. You have 30 days after receiving your item to request a return.\n</p><p>To be eligible for a return, your item must be in the same condition as received—unworn or unused, with tags, and in its original packaging. A receipt or proof of purchase is also required.\n</p><p>To start a return, kindly contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@teslaunch.net\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">support@teslaunch.net</a>.</p>",
            "question_4": "Q4:\"What should I do if I haven't received my package?\"",
            "answer_4": "<p>A4: 1. Confirm that the shipping address and email provided during the order are correct. If accurate, please check around your front door, back door, or nearby areas for the package.\n \n</p><p>2. If the package is not found, please contact your local carrier. Below are the contact details for major carriers:\n \n</p><p>1) USPS (US)\n Phone: 1-800-275-8777\n</p><p>Website: <a href=\"www.usps.com\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.usps.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Find a Post Office: Find Location\n \n</p><p></p><p>2) UPS (US)\n Phone: 1-888-742-5877\n</p><p>Website: <a href=\"www.ups.com\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.ups.com</a>.</p>\n \n<p></p><p> 3) OnTrac (US)\n Phone: 1-800-334-5000\n</p><p>Email: sagteam1@ontrac.com\n</p><p>Website: <a href=\"www.ontrac.com\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.ontrac.com</a>.</p>\n \n<p></p><p> 4) FedEx (US)\n Phone: 1-800-463-3339\n</p><p>Website: <a href=\"www.fedex.com\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.fedex.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Locate a FedEx Office: Find Location\n \n</p><p></p><p> 5) LaserShip (US)\n Phone: (804) 414-2590\n</p><p>Website: <a href=\"www.lasership.com\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.lasership.com</a>.</p>\n \n<p></p><p>6) Colis Privé (FR)\n Email: <a href=\"suividecolis@colisprive.com%20/%20opvolgenvanpakketten@colisprive.com\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">suividecolis@colisprive.com / opvolgenvanpakketten@colisprive.com</a>.</p>\n<p>Website: <a href=\"www.colisprive.be\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">www.colisprive.be</a>.</p><p></p>",
            "question_5": "Q5:\"What should I do if the product arrives damaged?\"",
            "answer_5": "<p>A5: Please provide pictures of the damaged product, the packaging, and your order number to our customer service team. We will verify with the shipping company and arrange a refund or replacement. Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@teslaunch.net\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">support@teslaunch.net</a>.</p>",
            "question_6": "Q6:\"Why did I only receive one item when I ordered multiple products?\"",
            "answer_6": "<p>A6: Orders with multiple items are often shipped in separate packages. Please check your shipment confirmation email, where you will find tracking numbers for each package.</p>",
